description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130985047.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran's IRGC has warned of a "heavy assault" on US military assets and ships if Iranian oil tankers or commercial vessels are attacked in the Strait of Hormuz. This follows US forces disabling two Iranian oil tankers in the Gulf of Oman and an earlier exchange of fire near the strait.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/missiles-drones-locked-on-us-targets-iran-warns-of-heavy-assault-after-tanker-strikes-in-gulf-of-oman/articleshow/130985047.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/missiles-drones-locked-on-us-targets-iran-warns-of-heavy-assault-after-tanker-strikes-in-gulf-of-oman/articleshow/130985047.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T06:19:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130985045,imgsize-1531995.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pakistani national among 3 arrested in US for attempting to smuggle 89 firearms into Canada]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130985113.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Three men, including a Pakistani national, face serious charges in the US for attempting to smuggle 89 firearms, many reportedly stolen, into Canada.  Authorities apprehended the trio during a traffic stop, uncovering a significant cache of weapons.  The accused are now detained, facing lengthy prison sentences for their alleged involvement in illegal arms trafficking.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/faizan-ali-25pakistani-national-among-3-arrested-in-us-for-attempting-to-smuggle-89-firearms-into-canada/articleshow/130985113.cms]